I"Ã	<p><a href="http://mediaelementjs.com/">mediaelement.js</a> is like magic. Itâ€™s browser and device support is perfect. To activate the video or audio player just set the following variable in front matter to <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">true</code>.</p>

